{"tid":1588941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"穿黑衣小巴乘客遭舉報帶署 梁振英感謝舉報者聲稱有賞","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T06:01:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"670b39dcf0678357a8b4a20f394b4f944875f2f8","tid":1588941,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1482047_1_L_20190923105129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1482047_1_L_20190923105129.jpg&h=40c6796b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前行政長官、全國政協副主席梁振英早前成立基金，懸紅獎賞舉報侮辱國旗國徽人士。他早上在社交網站貼文，上載一則報道，指懷疑有小巴司機舉報，令車上11名身穿黑衣的乘客，昨日在觀塘被警方截查並帶返警署。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在貼文中感謝舉報的人士，又提到無論「事前事後，一律有賞」。<br />\n<br />\n他早前接中新社訪問時亦提到，基金將開展第二波行動，希望徵集今次反修例運動背後資金及物資流向等信息。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482047-20190923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482047-20190923.htm&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=fcc99c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482047-20190923.htm&h=b3ec4436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482047-20190923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ae73c0df28f1417f9fd3bba9a7aaf44af9578bb6","tid":1588941,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"好呀,落地獄收啦"},{"pid":"ef1cf81b16fbf0bde33b30e5a0f2667d52c77b28","tid":1588941,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"47ed2287